<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RTI Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #000;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .form-field {
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            min-width: 200px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .field-value {
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #000;
            min-height: 20px;
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 5px;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">APPLICATION UNDER RIGHT TO INFORMATION ACT, 2005</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">TO:</div>
            <p><strong>The Public Information Officer</strong><br>
            {{ department_name | default('[Name of Department/Office]') }}<br>
            {{ department_address | default('[Address of Department/Office]') }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">APPLICANT DETAILS:</div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Name:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ applicant_name | default('[Your Full Name]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Address:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ applicant_address | default('[Your Complete Address]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Phone Number:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ phone_number | default('[Your Phone Number]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Email:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ email | default('[Your Email Address]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Date of Application:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ current_date }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">SUBJECT: {{ subject | default('Application for Information under RTI Act, 2005') }}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><strong>Sir/Madam,</strong></p>
            
            <p>I, {{ applicant_name | default('[Your Name]') }}, a citizen of India, hereby request the following information under the Right to Information Act, 2005:</p>
            
            <div class="section-title">INFORMATION REQUESTED:</div>
            <p>{{ information_requested | default('1. [Specify the exact information you need]\n2. [Be specific about documents, records, or data required]\n3. [Mention time period if applicable]\n4. [Any other relevant details]') }}</p>
            
            <div class="section-title">PURPOSE:</div>
            <p>{{ purpose | default('The information is required for [mention the purpose - personal use, research, public interest, etc.]') }}</p>
            
            <div class="section-title">MODE OF RECEIVING INFORMATION:</div>
            <p>{{ delivery_mode | default('Please provide the information in the following mode: [Hard copy/Email/Inspection of records]') }}</p>
            
            <p>I am enclosing an application fee of Rs. {{ application_fee | default('10') }} as prescribed under the RTI Act, 2005.</p>
            
            <p>If the information sought is not available with your office, kindly transfer this application to the concerned Public Information Officer under Section 6(3) of the RTI Act and inform me accordingly.</p>
            
            <p>If any additional fee is required, please inform me in advance with proper justification as per the RTI Act provisions.</p>
            
            <p>I request you to provide the information within the statutory period of 30 days as prescribed under Section 7(1) of the RTI Act, 2005.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><strong>Thanking you,</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="signature-line">
                    <div>{{ applicant_name | default('[Your Name]') }}</div>
                    <div>(Applicant)</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <div class="section-title">ENCLOSURES:</div>
            <p>1. Application fee of Rs. {{ application_fee | default('10') }}<br>
            2. {{ additional_documents | default('Any supporting documents (if applicable)') }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
